OL,3,CMurder investigation after man in his
OL,4,C20s dies following suspected assault
OL,6,FA murder investigation is underway
OL,7,Ffollowing a suspected assault in
OL,8,FNewcastle which has left a man dead.
OL,10,FNorthumbria Police were called to
OL,11,Freports of an assault on Shields Road,
OL,12,Fin Byker, at around 7.25pm on Tuesday
OL,13,F(16 June).
OL,15,FEmergency services found a man in his
OL,16,F20s with serious injuries. He was
OL,17,Ftaken to hospital for treatment but
OL,18,Fdied a short time later, police said.
OL,20,FHis next of kin have been told and are
OL,21,Fbeing supported by officers.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
