OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1782148757
OL,3,CMurder investigation after man in his
OL,4,C20s dies following suspected assault
OL,6,FThree people, two men aged 24 and 22
OL,7,Fand a 16-year-old boy, have been
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,10,FAs of Wednesday morning (17 June), a
OL,11,Fsignificant police presence remained
OL,12,Fat the scene, with a section of
OL,13,FShields Road closed to traffic.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Mark
OL,16,FAtherton, of the Force's Major
OL,17,FInvestigation Team, said: "This is a
OL,18,Ftragic incident, and our thoughts are
OL,19,Ffirmly with the family of the man who
OL,20,Fhas sadly lost his life.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
