OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1782148757
OL,3,CMurder investigation after man in his
OL,4,C20s dies following suspected assault
OL,6,F"We would like to reassure those in
OL,7,Fthe local community that our officers
OL,8,Fremain in the area to carry out a wide
OL,9,Frange of enquiries to ascertain
OL,10,Fexactly what happened.
OL,12,F"I would also ask anyone with
OL,13,Finformation regarding what took place
OL,14,Fyesterday evening to contact us."
OL,16,FOfficers are urging any witnesses, or
OL,17,Fanyone with information which could
OL,18,Fhelp their investigation, to get in
OL,19,Ftouch with them.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/3
